            "id": 6308838,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 永崴投控(3712)大漲7.23%，報26.7元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>永崴投控(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3712:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3712\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3712-TW</a>)13日11:10股價上漲1.8元，報26.7元，漲幅7.23%，成交2,779張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>永崴投控(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3712:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3712\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3712-TW</a>)所屬產業為電腦及週邊設備業，主要業務為H201010 一般投資業。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價上漲2.05%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲1.54%，股價波動與大盤表現同步。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+685 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+688 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-3 張</li> <li>融資增減：+53 張</li> <li>融券增減：-1 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
